<body><p>When you start the application for the first time, it will automatically open [[11 Devices|device selection dialog]]. You can connect to the device via Bluetooth and USB interfaces. To connect the device to a phone/tablet via USB, you need to use an On-The-Go (<span class="misspell-word">OTG</span>) cable.</p></body></html>